terminal packages. Also, use node scripts/build-all.mjs ciArtifacts for the CI-time build target; full pnpm build intentionally includes slower declaration package builds.'`\nEvidence after fix: focused Vitest shards passed 6/6; extension package boundary passed for 112 plugins plus 2 canaries in 102.1s; `ciArtifacts` build passed in 49.7s; full `pnpm build` passed in 195.3s; final autoreview reported no accepted/actionable findings.\nObserved result after fix: media/ACP helpers resolve from package boundaries, plugin SDK declarations stay resolvable, import cycles remain at 0, and core typecheck is green.\nWhat was not tested: no live provider/channel or cross-OS Crabbox run; this is an internal package-boundary refactor with local package, SDK, UI, build, and boundary proof.\n",
